{"tid":1355720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[元朗反恐打暴大遊行] 記住 入去唔係要復仇 係要保護元朗人！去除白色恐怖！","createTime":"2019-07-23T11:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T11:05:33.000Z","uid":218570,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd346a2c49d2dc5eba30caf8999d89aa4c750ec","tid":1355720,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"我明白大家好憤怒 好想做啲野<br />\n但記住 我地同白衫暴徒唔同 唔會無差別打村民<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只會自衛反抗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n727最重要係掃除白衫牛屎飛嘅陰霾<br />\n我地要比全香港 全世界睇到 只要團結<br />\n香港人係無所畏懼！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">民不畏死 奈何以死懼之</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再講咩燒村 拆祠堂 我地要光復嘅重點係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">人心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n只要萬眾一心 人數係我地最好啲矛與盾<br />\n<br />\n當然 有任何手足想做任何野 我地絕不割蓆<br />\n但記住 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好打開口牌 要做啲咩就做 Be water 入黑我地就散 </span></span><br />\n由得佢地成班三高圍村佬激到心臟病<br />\n贏 要一齊食住腦咁贏！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e3a8b6333096b99563dba90da74fb5f163eb9a6e","tid":1355720,"uid":218570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:03:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肅清官黑勾結 掃除白色恐怖</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a006742292ebe2c3fde3354ebaf0802efd3d453","tid":1355720,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"手快快打錯標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反恐抗暴大遊行至岩"},{"pid":"40483cf47ae1d96c3b87b54ed364d930c82e7e42","tid":1355720,"uid":255690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:05:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚再推何君堯 比人帶曬風向 推正經post"}]}